    "title": "Entry-Level Radiologist at AIIMS Delhi",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at AIIMS Delhi. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Radiologist to strengthen our Jodhpur-based team.\n\nAbout AIIMS Delhi:\nAIIMS Delhi is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with AIIMS Delhi!",
